Package: grpSLOPE
Type: Package
Title: Group SLOPE (Sorted L1 Penalized Estimation)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Alexej", "Gossmann", email = "alexej.go@googlemail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The Group SLOPE method can be used to select groups of predictor
    variables in a linear regression model with pre-specified group structures among
    the predictors, while controlling the (group-wise) false discovery rate at a
    user-specified level.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/agisga/grpSLOPE.git
